name: MXMetricManagerSubscriber
desc: A protocol defining a method for receiving a daily metrics report.

items.name: func didReceive([MXMetricPayload])
items.desc: Delivers new metrics reports to the object registered with the metrics manager.

items.name: func didReceive([MXDiagnosticPayload])
items.desc: Delivers new diagnostic reports to the object registered with the metrics manager.
